WEBVTT

00:02:27.956 --> 00:02:31.491
is unprecedented
in the history of humankind.

00:02:32.072 --> 00:02:35.410
We have estimated that by 2050,

00:02:35.434 --> 00:02:40.652
we have to build
700,000,000 more housing units,

00:02:40.676 --> 00:02:43.664
more than 300,000 schools

00:02:43.688 --> 00:02:47.677
and nearly 100,000 health centers.

00:02:49.173 --> 00:02:51.840
Let me put that into perspective for you.

00:02:52.902 --> 00:02:56.584
Every day for the next 35 years,

00:02:56.608 --> 00:02:59.521
we have to build seven health centers,

00:02:59.545 --> 00:03:01.403
25 schools